#### PR description:

Having checked with experts, this PR proposes to change the wfs we run in the short matrix:

- adding Run3 (2023) ZEE;
- adding ZeroBias and EGamma 2023D;
- removing 2021 express and prompt 2021;
- removing  .914 (since DB is already the default);
- removing .911 (mostly for XML checks, could be run in the IB tests only). 

This is just a first round of changes. Iteratively I will check if we can remove/add other wfs.

